=======

  *--[SHELL]----------------------------------------------------------------*
  |                                                                         |
  |  cd flens/examples                                                      |
  |  g++ -std=c++11 -Wall -I../.. -o lapack-trtri lapack-trtri.cc           |
  |                                                                         |
  *-------------------------------------------------------------------------*


